## Adjustments

Life happens, and it might happen that a lesson I planned to do in week 6 has to slide to week 7.
This section will record such adjustments that need to be made between full planning sessions.
The goal is not to make the syllabus liquid, but to give it the plasticity a living document needs in order not to break when it meets reality.

## North Star

Put notes here about the current "north star" or overall strategic vision of where we are working towards.
This may change over time, for example we may pivot from focusing on a very robust and high fluency in basic late republic grammar to the works of Cicero with thematic analysis, etc.
While this will evolve over time, this section is more inspirational, and may evolve slightly as we learn more about how I learn, how you teach, and the conventions that work well for us to work together.
This section does not need to be long or detailed, just very high level guidance so that we both no what we were thinking of on the horizon the last time we planned together.
